              <description><![CDATA[<h2>OLDS MOOC Final Reflective Post (Cloud)</h2>
<h3><strong>Signoff</strong></h3>
<p><strong>@30%</strong>. I wish to express my appreciation of Cloudworks even after just 10 days; it is indeed a departure from anything I had previously encountered, creative, minimalist and stable (Gr&aacute;inne Conole,&nbsp;<em>Juliette Culver</em>, Rebecca Galley,&nbsp;<em>Nick Freear</em>, Stephen Turvey and the tech team: cheers!).&nbsp;</p>
